<h3>2. Non-Essential Cookies</h3>
<p>These cookies add personalization and functionality but may collect personal data. Examples include tracking cookies used for analytics and advertising.</p>
<p>We comply with data privacy laws such as GDPR and CCPA when using non-essential cookies.</p>

